    slug: 'review-management-checklist-new-business',
    title: 'Review Management Checklist: New Business Starter Guide',
    titleZh: '評論管理檢查清單：新創事業入門指南',
    excerpt:
      'A complete review management checklist for new businesses. Learn how to set up your first reviews ethically, build a 90-day strategy, and use tools like QR codes to automate collection and boost local SEO.',
    excerptZh:
      '為新創企業提供的完整評論管理檢查清單。學習如何以符合道德的方式建立首批評論、制定90天策略，並運用QR碼等工具自動化收集流程，提升本地搜尋引擎優化成效。',
    category: 'guides',
